The following files are lifted verbatim from kbox/web/:
  - js/polling.js
  - js/state.js
  - js/chart.umd.min.js (Chart.js, see below)
  - style.css

The following files are adapted from kbox/web/ for box64_trace's data model:
  - index.html
  - js/gauges.js          (drawArc helper preserved verbatim)
  - js/events.js          (structure preserved, event types adapted)
  - js/main.js            (subset; drops kbox-specific tabs)
  - js/controls.js        (subset; pause-only)
  - js/telemetry.js       (no-op stub for kbox API surface)

